    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h3 id=\"h_01HWK3VH131PZ5F49S4JFV4XDK\"><span style=\"color: #434343;\">Added</span></h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><strong>TimePicker Filter for Console Logs:</strong> Introduced a TimePicker filter to the console logs, allowing users to select specific time ranges for log viewing, enhancing the usability and functionality of log analysis.<br>\n\t<img alt=\"\" height=\"324\" src=\"https://support.liferay.com/documents/d/customer-portal/26276963240461\" width=\"600\"></li>\n\t<li><strong>&nbsp;Geolocation Headers in Cloud Load Balancing: </strong>Enabled Cloud Load Balancing to inject geolocation information into HTTP headers, improving location-based content delivery and service customization for clients.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"h_01HWK3VH14GSPVM679PM24TXYY\"><span style=\"color: #434343;\">Bug Fixes</span></h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><strong>Backups List Pagination Fix:</strong> Fixed a bug where the pagination link did not function on the Backups list page, restoring full navigational functionality and improving the user experience in managing backups.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"h_01HWK3VH14GS3M4AVFSEHSF2VX\"><span style=\"color: #434343;\">Tasks</span></h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><strong>Mitigation of Curl Vulnerability in Backup Image: </strong>Addressed the Curl vulnerability (CVE-2023-38545) found in the backup image of the Liferay Cloud stack, enhancing security measures and protecting against potential exploits.</li>\n</ul>"
      },
